user.biography: we browse through instagram and feature poems and writings we enjoy reading ✨

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by poets of instagram on September 05, 2021 tagging @lonely.penguin. May be an image of text that says 'wish you could see yourself through these eyes and maybe then you would understand, how dearly loved you are and that my heart, soul, body and mind will always and forever belong to you. lonely. penguin'.

node.text:
If only you could see yourself the way I see you 🐚⠀
(cr: @lonely.penguin)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by poets of instagram on September 05, 2021 tagging @j.ironword. May be an image of text that says 'a I I want to know you in way that most do not. want to know your habits, your morning routines and night time rituals. I want to know what side of the bed you sleep on, the number of pillows that surround you and the cadence of your breathing. I want to be there to wish you sweet dreams and be beside you in case bad ones visit your subconscious, while always being there to kiss you good morning. j. iron word'.

Photo shared by poets of instagram on September 05, 2021 tagging @dthomasquotes. May be an image of text that says 'you don't get to choose the life you are given, but you do get to choose the way you live it. -Dane Thomas'.
